	* src/Makefile.am: updated
	* src/dt_date.c,
	* src/dt_date.h,
	* src/syntax.c: added a display type for dates (patch by
	pmhahn@debian.org)
	* src/formfill.h: register the display type (adjusted from the patch
	by pmhahn@debian.org)

